<div class="title">Avoiding the Initial Anxiety...</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B & Diazepam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DIEA&Exact=1">DIEA</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DIEA. "Avoiding the Initial Anxiety...: An Experience with 2C-B & Diazepam (exp20991)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 30, 2004. erowid.org/exp/20991</div>

<br/>



